@node history  "History"
@prev author
@next thanks
@toc main

  @{b}@{u}History@{ub}@{uu}

  @{b}*  1.2 :@{ub} (1/11/95)

  - Tooltype BCOLOR added. (Suggestion of Fergus O'Hea)

  - Tooltype LOCALE added. (Suggestion of Nils Goers & Pawel Hernik)
  
  - The program ends on double click in its window (the window being locked)
    (Suggestion of Alain Gaspard)
  
  - Deutsch doc & installer script translation (thanks to Nils Goers)


  @{b}*  1.1 :@{ub} (22/10/95)
  
  - While testing the german catalog from Nils Goers, I've found
  two strings that stayed untranslated.

  - English doc.

  - Modification of installer script to take account of the new german
  catalog.


  @{b}*  1.01:@{ub} (16/10/95)
    Correction of the following error:

    Changing of font that was resulting in the window growing was cutting
  some parts of the window if this one was too close from the screen edges.
    
  @{b}*  1.0 :@{ub} ( 7/10/95)
    First release.


